title: Evergreen Park closed to traffic
text:
Evergreen Park closed to traffic Sheboygan Press Media 4:11 p.m. CDT October 15, 2015 Corey Schjoth/Wausau Daily Herald Motorists traveling along the main roads in Mosinee canâ€™t help but notice construction signs through out the downtown area. (Photo: Sheboygan Press Media) CONNECT TWEET LINKEDIN COMMENT EMAIL MORE 
It was announced on Thursday that Evergreen Park has been closed to vehicle traffic for the season. 
Parking is available along Pine Grove Avenue. 
Additionally, city park restrooms were closed for the season with the exception of the outdoor restrooms at Deland Community Center, which will remain open throughout the year. Read or Share this story: http://shebpr.es/1LwiYqO TOP VIDEOS
